{"tid":2070393,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】單車美女意外翻車爆紅　真身是台灣豐滿網紅貝果","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:12:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f79a8ad6bef96d84ca60033b5a036e49c0a9ea2","tid":2070393,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"近日台灣發生一宗交通意外，竟然成為網上熱搜，事緣一名身穿吊帶背心的少女，騎單車時意外翻車，嚇得花容失色，雖然她未有洩露春光，但驕人上圍已經呼之欲出，網民瘋狂搜尋該名少女真身，經起底後才知她是台灣網紅貝果(Bagel)，而她亦在IG回應，指自己在騎單車轉彎時摔倒，卻沒有受太大的傷，粉絲知道之後即時放下心頭大石。"},{"pid":"650a0e30f3eee1a017415f0698beb183581822f6","tid":2070393,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200618/350340570205523968.jpeg/ctPBG9l5fa-sOH9l2JZf4sByuaahB2dUJXjl9yV45fc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200618%2F350340570205523968.jpeg%2FctPBG9l5fa-sOH9l2JZf4sByuaahB2dUJXjl9yV45fc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0f4f9bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7b49ba5bf8f15579f0eb9763c71e8ef1259408","tid":2070393,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200618/350340662849310720.jpeg/L2qP736eLBE91_gC7ZElK_YQ6iFF_0kpvpgNlb6YDZU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200618%2F350340662849310720.jpeg%2FL2qP736eLBE91_gC7ZElK_YQ6iFF_0kpvpgNlb6YDZU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f69eb7ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200618/350340664946462720.jpeg/WE-BQoyYzyvGiKrDAocWlJ9ph2EYDwCGjt9WP47fVj8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%